{"tid":2218281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【俄羅斯醫療事故】剖腹產驚見女兒臉被刀割傷破相 醫生辯稱：女嬰不應該亂動","createTime":"2020-09-26T06:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T07:08:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63e4e731cdbe62a4240dbaa3101b3d6410c35899","tid":2218281,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:06:58.000Z","msg":"懷胎10個月，最期待見到新生兒。惟俄羅斯一名19歲新手媽媽選擇剖腹產後，卻驚見初生女兒臉上有一道長約3厘米傷口，原來是醫生不慎割傷，但卻辯稱因女嬰亂動所致。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，俄羅斯19歲準媽媽Darya Kadochnikova，原打算到當地一間公立醫院進行自然分娩，惟生產前醫生告知胎位不正，故建議剖腹生產。<br />\n<br />\n剖腹產時，醫生為Darya進行全身麻醉，但她在生產過過程中仍能感覺到一切，醫生遂為她注射靜脈麻醉藥，她原以為一切都會順利，並期待新生命誕生。「我只希望女兒可平安出生就好」。<br />\n<br />\n豈料當她麻醉消退醒來，赫然發現女兒的臉上有一道約3厘米的傷口，傷疤周圍的皮膚更呈青綠色。<br />\n<br />\nDarya向醫生追問原因，對方始透露在進行剖腹手術期間，意外割傷女嬰臉部，導致其右眼下方留下一道疤痕。<br />\n&quot;因為嬰兒在剖腹過程中，突然扭動，所以導致手術刀劃過女嬰的臉，女嬰不應該亂郁動。&quot;<br />\n<br />\nDarya認為不能原諒涉事醫生的疏失，她在受訪時稱：<br />\n&quot;女兒臉上的傷口非常深，範圍亦很大，很大機會留下疤痕。等女兒長大後，再另做手術。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n她續指，事後已向專業人士諮詢意見，對方向她指意外屬醫療事故，可向醫院追究責任，她已向涉事醫院作出投訴，惟院方一直未有回應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2763479/daughter_thumb_20200926_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2763479%2Fdaughter_thumb_20200926_J_1024.jpg&h=8b1012d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"752c05267657d0bb5a369ab40e1f870186717a6b","tid":2218281,"uid":1067,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OqMRiXM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqMRiXM.png&h=809293d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de26f2710893b628f9979910ceea8d8262f9bdf3","tid":2218281,"uid":309989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:13:48.000Z","msg":"BB好慘"},{"pid":"53cf602f4e38288ba1086978b33208dd797ccecf","tid":2218281,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de26f2710893b628f9979910ceea8d8262f9bdf3","tid":2218281,"uid":309989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:13:48.000Z","msg":"BB好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81def8bf3fdb88bff6e37d8728bc6e266ab6d84d","tid":2218281,"uid":377787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"752c05267657d0bb5a369ab40e1f870186717a6b","tid":2218281,"uid":1067,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OqMRiXM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqMRiXM.png&h=809293d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"責任全在嬰方"},{"pid":"e59a274dd122c9ed19f6d0294049fafe41c22979","tid":2218281,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"醫生又肯定唔係有心嘅, 不過柒左咪認<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658047e26d67b3681c4f412d2782ef4dc1de7dd6","tid":2218281,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"以為hi到少少，笑左<br />\n點知原來真係咁深<br />\n希望初生復原能力高d會冇事"}]}